data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER. FHA LOAN IS ASSUMABLE AT THE INCREDIBLE RATE OF 2.375% Welcome to your dream home in Eagle Mountain! This stunning 2020 build is nestled in a serene neighborhood, perfectly situated between Cedar Valley High School and Cory Wride Memorial Park. Move-in ready, this home is better than buying new as it comes with more than $90K in upgrades, completed yard and fully equipped with appliances, making your transition seamless. Step inside to discover the heart of the home, featuring a custom gas fireplace adorned with floor-to-ceiling tile and a built-in bookshelf. The gourmet kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, complete with a Bosch fridge, oversized island, Spanish quartz countertops, and a striking herringbone backsplash. GE smart appliances add a modern touch, while the black quartz undercounter sink exudes elegance. Upgraded lighting, soft-close cabinets, trim, flooring, and fixtures throughout the home add an extra layer of sophistication. Experience the convenience of a smart home with both a Ring doorbell and smart thermostat included. With tasteful upgrades and design choices, every detail has been considered. This residence offers the perfect combination of both luxury and functionality. The fully fenced yard, complete with garden boxes and a relaxing patio, provides privacy and space for your green thumb. A double door gate opens up to the side yard to provide a secure place to park a small camper. The basement is a canvas awaiting your personal touch, promising increased value to your investment with the potential to add 2-3 bedrooms and an additional bathroom. If desired, the upstairs loft could also be converted to a bedroom, for a total potential of 7 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional house your forever home. Schedule a showing and experience the lifestyle this Eagle Mountain gem has to offer!
